[section#dcl.init.string
    [:en] Character arrays
    [:zh_CN] 字符数组

[%  [:en] initialization[!character array]
    [:zh_CN] 初始化[!字符数组] ]
]

[para]
[:en]
An array of ordinary character type ([#basic.fundamental]), [`char8_t] array,
[`char16_t] array, [`char32_t] array, or [`wchar_t] array can be initialized by
an ordinary string literal, UTF-8 string literal, UTF-16 string literal, UTF-32
string literal, or wide string literal, respectively, or by an
appropriately-typed string literal enclosed in braces ([#lex.string]).
[:zh_CN]
普通字符类型的数组（[#basic.fundamental]），[`char8_t] 数组，[`char16_t] 数组，
[`char32_t] 数组，或者 [`wchar_t] 数组可以分别用普通字符串字面量，UTF-8 字符串
字面量，UTF-16 字符串字面量，UTF-32 字符串字面量，或者宽字符串字面量初始化，或者
用由花括号包围的相应类型的字符串字面量初始化（[#lex.string]）。

[:en]
[%initialization[!character array]]
Successive characters of the value of the string literal initialize the elements
of the array.
[:zh_CN]
[%初始化[!字符数组]]
字符串字面量中的字符依次初始化数组的元素。

[enter:example]
[codeblock]
char msg[] = "Syntax error on line %s\n";
[codeblock:end]

[:en]
shows a character array whose members are initialized with a [~string-literal].
[:zh_CN]
展示了一个其成员用[~字符串字面量]初始化的字符数组。

[:en]
Note that because [`'\n'] is a single character and because a trailing [`'\0']
is appended, [`sizeof(msg)] is [`25].
[:zh_CN]
注意，由于 [`'\n'] 为单个字符且由于添加了尾部 [`'\0']，[`sizeof(msg)] 是 [`25]。
[exit:example]

[para]
[:en]
There shall not be more initializers than there are array elements.
[:zh_CN]
初始化式不能多于数组元素。

[enter:example]
[codeblock]
char cv[4] = "asdf";            // [:en] error
                                // [|:zh_CN] 错误
[codeblock:end]

[:en]
is ill-formed since there is no space for the implied trailing [`'\0'].
[:zh_CN]
是非良构的，这是因为没有隐含的 [`'\0'] 的位置。
[exit:example]

[para]
[:en]
If there are fewer initializers than there are array elements, each element not
explicitly initialized shall be zero-initialized ([#dcl.init]).
[:zh_CN]
如果初始化式比数组元素少，则每个未显式初始化的元素应当被零初始化（[#dcl.init]）。
